thread.title: Angela Marshall
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Angela Marshall

author: Angela Marshall
title: Angela Marshall
text: We had always bought out replacement ink cartridges at our local PO but discovered that they had ceased stocking the Canon cartridges we required when we turned up to replace the latest empties. Found Inkstation on- line and ordered a batch of them that day. They arrived on the next business day which was terrific. Very satisfied customers.
